{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-012__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-012", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-012__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·012.1", "text_original": "彼狡童兮，不與我言兮，維子之故，使我不能餐兮。\n彼狡童兮，不與我食兮，維子之故，使我不能息兮。", "text_normalized": "彼狡童兮，不與我言兮，維子之故，使我不能餐兮。\n彼狡童兮，不與我食兮，維子之故，使我不能息兮。", "notes": "狡童 Chinese poem 1."}
